plham

Class Order

  • plham.Order
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Cancel

    public class Order
    A data structure for orders.

    Specify

    • Type (kind): {buy, sell} x {limit, market}
    • Price
    • Volume
    • Expiry time (relative)
